featured_reviews.review_id: Hai to ghar ke bagal me par kabhie bulaya nahi unhone namaaz padhne ke liye, ab kuraan shreef padh loon to jaa ke milu.. tab to samjh me aaye ki wahan karna kya hai. Baaki sabhi muslim bhai log ek dum tip top hokar har shukarwar ko namaz padhne jaate hain.. aur kuch log daily, baaki apan to 5 baar din me azaan sun hi lete hain... Thodi thodi to main bhi seekh gaya hoon...

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: He has never called people in front of the house to offer Namaz, now after reading the Holy Quran, he went to Loon.. then he understood what to do. All the rest of the Muslim brothers go to pray on Friday wearing a tip top.. and a few people daily, the rest of them recite Azaan 5 times a day... I too have learned a little...
